Project 16: OR Block Schedule Management System
 Every hospital loses millions in OR revenue through underutilized block time - surgeons hold reserved OR blocks they don't fill, while other surgeons can't get cases scheduled. This platform owns the entire lifecycle of OR block allocation, utilization tracking, and release workflows, making it one of the most financially impactful operational systems in a surgical hospital.
Modules: Block Allocation Engine, Surgeon Block Portfolio, Utilization Tracking, Block Release Workflow, Waitlist & Backfill Engine, Case Volume Forecasting, Block Reallocation Approval, Notification Service, OR Director Dashboard, Audit History
